channel.title: Clue Scrolls
channel.description:
If you've ever seen the clue scroll code for delta: [code] case 2856: c.sM("I can only open this at the exact spot at Camelot bank!"); break; [/code] I want to know where I can edit the spot to dig. Any help?
-Pblord7

item.title: Clue Scrolls
item.dc:creator: @youridudock youridudock
item.description:
@youridudock wrote:

[quote=“Pblord7, post:5, topic:372152”][quote author=youridudock link=topic=468213.msg3423119#msg3423119 date=1291678342]

If you’ve ever seen the clue scroll code for delta:

case 2856:
c.sM("I can only open this at the exact spot at Camelot bank!");
break;

I want to know where I can edit the spot to dig. Any help?

-Pblord7

easy. Go find the spot and do ::mypos so u know your coords. then search it in Client.java/Clickingmost.java etc.
Sorry that i cant say the right spot but i am tired and ive got no sourchs on this computer!

Got it…
Its in Potions.java

Yay
[/quote]
As in you didn’t help me[/quote]

-.- i am happy for u
